net.enilink.composition.asm.meta

Class ClassInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.objectweb.asm.ClassVisitor
      • net.enilink.composition.asm.meta.ClassInfo

  • public class ClassInfo
extends org.objectweb.asm.ClassVisitor
    Reflective meta data for classes that also contains the visible and invisible annotations of their methods.

    • Field Detail

      • version

        public int version
        The class version.

      • access

        public int access
        The class's access flags (see Opcodes). This field also indicates if the class is deprecated.

      • name

        public String name
        The internal name of the class (see getInternalName).

      • signature

        public String signature
        The signature of the class. Mayt be null.

      • superName

        public String superName
        The internal of name of the super class (see getInternalName). For interfaces, the super class is Object. May be null, but only for the Object class.

      • interfaces

        public List<String> interfaces
        The internal names of the class's interfaces (see getInternalName). This list is a list of String objects.

      • methods

        public Map<org.objectweb.asm.commons.Method,org.objectweb.asm.tree.MethodNode> methods
        The methods of this class.

      • visibleAnnotations

        public List<org.objectweb.asm.tree.AnnotationNode> visibleAnnotations
        The runtime visible annotations of this class. This list is a list of AnnotationNode objects. May be null.

      • invisibleAnnotations

        public List<org.objectweb.asm.tree.AnnotationNode> invisibleAnnotations
        The runtime invisible annotations of this class. This list is a list of AnnotationNode objects. May be null.
